'''邁克·赫爾利'''（{{lang-en|Myke Hurley}}）是一名來自[[英國|英國]]的專業全職[[播客|播客]]錄製者<ref>{{Cite web|title = imyke's Tweet|url = https://twitter.com/imyke/status/519855729352929280|website = Twitter|accessdate = 2016-01-20|archive-date = 2015-10-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151009034720/https://twitter.com/imyke/status/519855729352929280|dead-url = no}}</ref>。他在2011年創辦播客網絡70Decibels，後來該網絡於2013年3月被{{le|5by5|5by5}}收購<ref>{{cite web|last1=Gonzales|first1=Chris|title=Talking About the Things We Love: An Interview with Myke Hurley|url=http://www.sparkjournal.net/blog/2013/7/22/myke-hurley-interview|website=sparkjournal.net|publisher=sparkjournal.net|accessdate=18 November 2015|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112010954/https://www.sparkjournal.net/blog/2013/7/22/myke-hurley-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref>。期後，他與[[斯蒂芬·哈克特|斯蒂芬·哈克特]]（Stephen M. Hackett）在2014年8月18日創立了另一個播客網絡[[Relay_FM|Relay FM]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hackett|first1=Stephen|title=A year of Relay FM|url=http://www.extras.relay.fm/blog/2015/8/4/a-year-of-relay|website=Relay FM|publisher=RelayFM|accessdate=18 November 2015|archive-date=2019-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427001811/https://www.extras.relay.fm/blog/2015/8/4/a-year-of-relay|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

蘋果公司於它的播客系列「Events at the Apple Store」中-{zh-hant:訪問;zh-hans:访问}-了赫爾利<ref>{{Cite web|title = How I Became an Independent Podcaster by Events at the Apple Store on iTunes|url = https://itunes.apple.com/gb/podcast/how-i-became-independent-podcaster/id975601115?mt=2|website = iTunes|accessdate = 2015-11-27|archive-date = 2018-12-15|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181215124827/https://itunes.apple.com/gb/podcast/how-i-became-independent-podcaster/id975601115?mt=2|dead-url = no}}</ref>，他在該節目內分享了他如何成為一名全職播客錄製者。

